Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-vit-fpga layer to your build

I. Adding the meta-vit-fpga layer to your build
=================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-vit-fpga'
Add 'IMAGE_INSTALL:append = " grow-home"' to your local.conf
